Actor and comedian, Ime Bishop Umoh aka Okon Lagos has offered a distinction between those he described as true leaders and true politicians. According to him, “A true leader thinks about the next generation while a true politician thinks about the next election. Read Also : Banky W, Atiku, perfect illustration of disqualification by association – Okon Lagos “They just don’t care! If they do, it’s ALL about themselves and NONE about you! “ While criticising politicians, the comic star urged people to always care for themselves at all times. He added; “Take care of yourself at all times. Naija politicians no be am o. #okonlagos #okonrepublic #iyammi #chisos #wosappen #okonofiaflagosz.”